ratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016179, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, bless Muhammad and the progeny of Muhammad and forgive and give us salvation that is absolute. O Allah, I ask You by Your treasured name…that You forgive all my sins. I ask You by the right of Muhammad and his purified progeny that You forgive my great sins. O Allah, I have committed evil and oppressed my self, so forgive me. O God, You are excessively forgiving and You also like forgiveness; so now forgive me.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "اے اللہ حضرت محمد کو اس کی اتنی جزا دے جس کا وہ حقدار ہیں تو خداوند عالم اس کے ستر سال کے گناہ معاف فرمائے گا اور بے حساب ثواب عطا کرے گا۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN, WAGH FIR LANAA MAGHFERATN JAZMAN. ALLAAHUMMA INNEE AS-ALOKA BISMEKAL MAKHZOONE… AN TAGHFERA LEE KULLA ZANBIN. AS-ALOKA BEHAQQE MOHAMMADIN WA AALEHIT TAAHEREENA AN TAGHFERA LEE ZANBEYAL A’ZEEMA. ALLAAHUMMA A’MILTO SOO-AN, WA ZALAMTO NAFSEE, FAGH FIR LEE. ALLAAHUMMA INNEKA A’FUWWUN TOHIBBUL A’FWA FA’FO A’NNEE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰہُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ، وَاغْفِرْ لَنَا مَغْفِرَةً جَزْمًا۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ اِنِّیْ اَسْئَلُكَ بِاسْمِكَ الْمَخْزُوْنِ۔ اَنْ تَغْفِرَ لِیْ كُلَّ ذَنْبٍ۔ اَسْئَلُكَ بِحَقِّ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِہِ الطَّاہِرِیْن اَنْ تَغْفِرَ لِیْ ذَنْبِیَ الْعَظِیْمَ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ عَمِلْتُ سُوْۗءً، وَظَلَمْتُ نَفْسِیْ، فَاغْفِرْ لِیْ۔ اَللّٰہُمَّ اِنَّكَ عَفُوٌّ تُحِبُّ الْعَفْوَ فَاعْفُ عَنِّیْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null,